## 9. Summary report format

After running all sections, output a table:

```
SECTION                        STATUS   NOTES
─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
1. Python static analysis      PASS
2. Topic contract              PASS
3. JSON schema spot-check      WARN     <specific key if mismatch>
4. Docker build                PASS
5. Docker Compose schema       PASS
6. Upload endpoint             PASS
7. Frontend JS sanity          PASS
8. Arm state machine           PASS
─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
OVERALL                        PASS     (or FAIL if any FAIL)
```

For every FAIL or WARN, add a one-line fix suggestion directly below the table row.
